					<!--This Section has 4 entries, 1 for each order type on the National POLST form (A,B,C,D.). These entry templates are Acts and each is related to a Procedure entry template.-->
					<!-- TO DW:  If you add the Planned Procedure Section as Implied, then you will also add the templateID here -->
